- Bravo!

978
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:07,820
[Qizhou Ziwan]

979
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:09,780
Wang.

980
00:40:10,660 --> 00:40:11,380
Ma'am.

981
00:40:12,180 --> 00:40:13,060
How's business today?

982
00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:14,420
Let me tell you,

983
00:40:14,580 --> 00:40:16,100
several groups of customers came today.

984
00:40:16,100 --> 00:40:17,340
The prices offered were quite high.

985
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:20,100
The highest offer
was four jiao per jin.

986
00:40:20,380 --> 00:40:21,460
But as you instructed,

987
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,540
I sent them all away.

988
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:23,380
OK.

989
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:25,500
Ma'am,

990
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:26,420
I wonder,

991
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:28,500
what's the real price
you're willing to sell at?

992
00:40:31,060 --> 00:40:31,580
I...

993
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,340
There's a customer, Ma'am.

994
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:35,900
Who's in charge?

995
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:41,220
It's you?

996
00:40:41,460 --> 00:40:43,100
Mr. Yi, long time no see.

997
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:45,900
It's been a while.
Seems you've made something of yourself.

998
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:47,100
So that's why

999
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:50,940
I haven't seen

1000
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:51,900
any Qizhou Ziwan around.

1001
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:53,060
Turns out you've got it all.

1002
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:53,980
Please take a seat.

1003
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:58,060
Yes, over 100,000 jin in total.

1004
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:01,700
You've got piles of it.

1005
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:03,900
Can you sell it all?

1006
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:06,060
And yet, here you are.

1007
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:08,140
Yeah, right.

1008
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:09,100
I heard

1009
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:10,540
