I'll take the whole lot.

1015
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:19,380
The latest price for Ziwan

1016
00:41:19,380 --> 00:41:20,660
is four jiao per jin.

1017
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:21,940
And it's hard to buy even then.

1018
00:41:23,620 --> 00:41:25,180
You'd believe such rumors?

1019
00:41:26,100 --> 00:41:27,100
Honestly,

1020
00:41:27,380 --> 00:41:30,260
