1024
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:43,420
Is that so?

1025
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,100
Let's not talk about this anymore.

1026
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:51,100
I'm not unreasonable.

1027
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:54,260
You're young, widowed.

1028
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:55,220
It hasn't been easy.

1029
00:41:55,500 --> 00:41:57,740
So I'll raise the price by one jiao.

1030
00:41:58,460 --> 00:41:59,420
Three jiao per jin.

1031
00:41:59,740 --> 00:42:01,020
If you can sell at that price,

1032
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:02,100
I'll buy.

1033
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:03,980
If you think it's not fair,

1034
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:05,180
I won't argue.

1035
00:42:05,620 --> 00:42:07,700
I'll deal with the herb farmers
in Mingguan Town.

1036
00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:10,580
Every batch of Ziwan from there
is under my control.

1037
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:15,180
Then Zhengzhang Town.

1038
00:42:15,540 --> 00:42:17,500
That's mine too.

1039
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:29,380
I don't believe it.

1040
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:30,620
Should I

1041
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:32,980
show you the contracts I signed

1042
00:42:32,980 --> 00:42:33,940
with those local herb farmers?

1043
00:42:35,060 --> 00:42:35,940
No need.

1044
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:38,100
A contract
is just about putting a handprint.

1045
00:42:38,260 --> 00:42:39,740
I believe you on this.

1046
00:42:40,260 --> 00:42:42,820
You're really something.

1047
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,380
Thank you for the compliment.

1048
00:42:45,860 --> 00:42:47,260
Alright then,

1049
00:42:47,860 --> 00:42:49,060
I'll add another jiao for you.

1050
00:42:49,380 --> 00:42:50,260
Four jiao.

1051
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:52,780
That's double last year's price.

1052
00:42:53,220 --> 00:42:54,620
Apologies, Mr. Yi.

1053
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:57,140
This year's Ziwan is not for sale.

